s, and show evidence for supernova driven\nexpansions. Remnants of these associations have now been identified by Gaia,\nshowing that traces of star-forming structures can persist for a few hundred\nmillion years.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Mar 2022 19:00:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-04"}
