structural perturbations -- without any fine-tuning of global\nparameters -- joins explosive synchronization and percolation under the same\nmechanistic framework.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Mar 2022 21:28:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-02"}
