recent result for functionals. Finally, our results\nfind important applications, among which we point out that we solve a proposed\nopen problem showing that the unique predual of the space of Lipschitz\nfunctions from the Euclidean unit circle fails to have Lindenstrauss property\nA.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Mar 2022 11:30:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-02"}
