upports our theory regarding the moderating role of ideology.\nStill, surprisingly, our findings suggest that the negative effect of populism\non entrepreneurship is greater in nations with stronger checks and balances.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Mar 2022 14:10:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-09"}
