ty of the bismuth\noxido cluster in a protic as well as an aprotic polar organic solvent and the\ngrowth mode of the clusters on Au upon spin-, dip-, and drop-coating on gold\nsurfaces were studied. Successful deposition of bismuth oxido cluster was\nproven by powder XRD, FTIR, and XPS while the microstructure of the resulting\nfilms was investigated as a function of the deposition method and the solvent\nused by SEM, AFM, and optical microscopy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Mar 2022 15:28:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 22 Mar 2022 08:10:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-23"}
